{"tid":25281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7警黃祖成：被打不是曾健超  法官聽罷皺起眉","createTime":"2016-12-06T04:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T13:28:02.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5e208721fcbea54ecb1f2559ccc3584933409690","tid":25281,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:36:01.000Z","msg":"7名警員涉於佔領期間在添馬公園變電站暗角位置，毆打公民黨成員曾健超案，辯方今開始結案陳詞，代表黃祖成的資深大狀駱應淦質疑在暗角片段中被打的人根本不是曾健超，可能是同晚行動中被捕的另一名示威者。法官聽罷皺起眉，即席播放多段影片，著控辯雙方認一認被抬的人身上的黑色上衣和白色鞋是否與曾的衣著相同，例如被打者衣服背面有花紋。駱看片後表示，單憑衣著認人很危險，這些衣著特徵不是曾健超獨有。"},{"pid":"19d1f293e63e913bd4511827445c1cedbcc3853f","tid":25281,"uid":7692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:36:57.000Z","msg":"影武者得川家康"},{"pid":"a5cb1134b1cffd601ff8e4f50d9c789eed544c92","tid":25281,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:37:59.000Z","msg":"法官心諗 屌 你咁都講得出"},{"pid":"a5d966c03cb7d625efc56cc4175899e35f8eec89","tid":25281,"uid":26076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:38:23.000Z","msg":"被打既唔係佢就可以打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食屎啦黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e64f8a8c07c73c9511afb3e3f53edd8c008ca4","tid":25281,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:38:39.000Z","msg":"真係諗住攣都拗直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4afa356929d3145cd9bd2673f661a3b75ffd739c","tid":25281,"uid":48381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:38:57.000Z","msg":"咁係未姐係認左打人？"},{"pid":"8238c7d0a22fe31224e0c77e4875fdf8f967329b","tid":25281,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:39:13.000Z","msg":"垃圾黑警橫死掂死賴第二位搏無罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49fba8d9769acd0dc48567082831021e96407ea1","tid":25281,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci