,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:43:47.000Z","msg":"on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ec7f4aba34e00cf80f5c8728fd8b298a9b5d0c","tid":25281,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:43:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d1060a7cf75d792e3c2e1efd4f981b2e35a8a83","tid":25281,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:44:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戇鳩 咁係咪可以告多單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好傻啦 打甩左依單 佢地過左海就係神仙"},{"pid":"f9a23d4d2d5d1b6731bb22f4ac779b317a394048","tid":25281,"uid":25882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:46:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁認打人有咩意思</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n推到去佢地唔係打曾健超<br />\n咁即係呢單案佢地會無罪<br />\n你想告佢就搵番個受害者出黎或者告佢第二條<br />\n然後又可增以拖佢幾十年"},{"pid":"63e8e76e80575a68671168c8fb4bef6da7f0e1c3","tid":25281,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:46:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>戇鳩 咁係咪可以告多單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好傻啦 打甩左依單 佢地過左海就係神仙</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪就係，佢地打咁耐都主要係打認人既問題，個官confirm唔到被打果個係曾健超，又打曾健超認唔到佢7個。<br />\n係仆街，但係有用"},{"pid":"4854910e72a7b289137560cebcfe5a8600f14889","tid":25281,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:46:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個官心諗: 屌你老母咁都講得出</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你同我留既言幾乎一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdad15138d109a7b256fdace0610a4311fd4f611","tid":25281,"uid":41198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:47:15.000Z","msg":"咁係咪已經認左蓄意傷人罪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/